# .raw-exemptions/raw_6.list — grandfather list for raw#6 (F4 generic-dir)
# format: <path_prefix_or_file> | <line_range> | <reason> | <expiry YYYY-MM-DD>
# expiry REQUIRED — indefinite grandfather forbidden.
#
# raw#6 bans 7 generic basenames: utils helpers common lib misc stuff base.
# F4 scanner = basename-only match. Valid module paths whose dir basename
# happens to land on one of those names are whitelisted here via path-prefix
# (any path containing /<prefix> as a segment is exempt).
#
# 2026-04-26 anima seed entry — single F4 hit.

# scripts/lib — runtime container for shell+hexa snippets sourced by
# growth.hexa, deploy.hexa and the cron wrappers. The folder is a
# stable namespace (multi-file, F5-clean other than growth_common.hexa
# which is in raw_7.list as a research-iterative loner). Renaming to
# `scripts/libs/` would break ~12 cross-script source paths and the
# launchd plist invocations. jurisdiction-out: deploy. owner: anima.
# audit 2026-04-26: 12-month review cycle (expiry 2027-04-26).
scripts/lib/    | * | runtime container for sourced shell+hexa snippets — rename breaks cross-script paths [jurisdiction-out: deploy] — owner: anima | 2027-04-26
